{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.1","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 10:1","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.009.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.010.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Paul d\u00e9fend son minist\u00e8re<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-11: cf. 1 Co 2:1-5. Ro 15:17-19. 2 Co 6:4-7; 13:2-4, 10.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.10.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Moi Paul, je vous prie, par la douceur et la bont\u00e9 de Christ, moi, humble d\u2019apparence quand je suis au milieu de vous, et plein de hardiesse \u00e0 votre \u00e9gard quand je suis \u00e9loign\u00e9,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.2","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.9.15","name":"2 Corinthiens 9:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.9.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.2","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 10:2","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.010.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.010.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.10.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>je vous prie, lorsque je serai pr\u00e9sent, de ne pas me forcer \u00e0 recourir avec assurance \u00e0 cette hardiesse, dont je me propose d\u2019user contre quelques-uns qui nous regardent comme marchant selon la chair.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.3","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.1","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.3","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 10:3","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.010.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.010.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.10.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Si nous marchons dans la chair, nous ne combattons pas selon la chair.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.4","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.2","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.4","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 10:4","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.010.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.010.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.10.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Car les armes avec lesquelles nous combattons ne sont pas charnelles; mais elles sont puissantes, par la vertu de Dieu, pour renverser des forteresses.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.5","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.3","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.5","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 10:5","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.010.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.010.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.10.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Nous renversons les raisonnements et toute hauteur qui s\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve contre la connaissance de Dieu, et nous amenons toute pens\u00e9e captive \u00e0 l\u2019ob\u00e9issance de Christ.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.6","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.4","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.6","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 10:6","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.010.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.010.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.10.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Nous sommes pr\u00eats aussi \u00e0 punir toute d\u00e9sob\u00e9issance, lorsque votre ob\u00e9issance sera compl\u00e8te.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.7","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.5","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.7","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 10:7","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.010.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.010.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.10.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Vous regardez \u00e0 l\u2019apparence! Si quelqu\u2019un se persuade qu\u2019il est de Christ, qu\u2019il se dise bien en lui-m\u00eame que, comme il est de Christ, nous aussi nous sommes de Christ.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.6","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.8","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 10:8","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.010.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.010.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.10.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Et quand m\u00eame je me glorifierais un peu trop de l\u2019autorit\u00e9 que le Seigneur nous a donn\u00e9e pour votre \u00e9dification et non pour votre destruction, je ne saurais en avoir honte,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.7","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.9","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 10:9","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.010.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.010.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.10.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>afin que je ne paraisse pas vouloir vous intimider par mes lettres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.8","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.10","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 10:10","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.010.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.010.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.10.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Car, dit-on, ses lettres sont s\u00e9v\u00e8res et fortes; mais, pr\u00e9sent en personne, il est faible, et sa parole est m\u00e9prisable.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.11","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.9","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.11","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 10:11","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.010.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.010.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.10.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Que celui qui parle de la sorte consid\u00e8re que tels nous sommes en paroles dans nos lettres, \u00e9tant absents, tels aussi nous sommes dans nos actes, \u00e9tant pr\u00e9sents.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.12","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.12","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 10:12","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.010.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.010.013,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 12-18: cf. Ro 15:17-21. 1 Co 15:9, 10.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.10.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>\n    Nous n\u2019osons pas nous \u00e9galer ou nous comparer \u00e0 quelques-uns de ceux qui se recommandent eux-m\u00eames. Mais, en se mesurant \u00e0 leur propre mesure et en se comparant \u00e0 eux-m\u00eames, ils manquent d\u2019intelligence.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.13","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.11","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.13","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 10:13","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.010.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.010.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.10.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Pour nous, nous ne voulons pas nous glorifier hors de toute mesure; nous prendrons, au contraire, pour mesure les limites du partage que Dieu nous a assign\u00e9, de mani\u00e8re \u00e0 nous faire venir aussi jusqu\u2019\u00e0 vous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.14","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.12","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.14","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 10:14","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.010.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.010.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.10.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Nous ne d\u00e9passons point nos limites, comme si nous n\u2019\u00e9tions pas venus jusqu\u2019\u00e0 vous; car c\u2019est bien jusqu\u2019\u00e0 vous que nous sommes arriv\u00e9s avec l\u2019\u00c9vangile de Christ.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.15","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.13","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.15","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 10:15","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.010.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.010.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.10.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Ce n\u2019est pas hors de toute mesure, ce n\u2019est pas des travaux d\u2019autrui, que nous nous glorifions; mais c\u2019est avec l\u2019esp\u00e9rance, si votre foi augmente, de grandir encore d\u2019avantage parmi vous, selon les limites qui nous sont assign\u00e9es,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.16","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.14","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.16","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 10:16","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.010.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.010.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.10.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>et d\u2019annoncer l\u2019\u00c9vangile au-del\u00e0 de chez vous, sans nous glorifier de ce qui a \u00e9t\u00e9 fait dans les limites assign\u00e9es \u00e0 d\u2019autres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.17","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.15","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.17","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 10:17","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.010.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.010.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.10.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Que celui qui se glorifie se glorifie dans le Seigneur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.18","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.16","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.18","label":"","reference":"2 Corinthiens 10:18","prev_osis_id":"2Cor.010.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Cor.011.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Cor.10.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Car ce n\u2019est pas celui qui se recommande lui-m\u00eame qui est approuv\u00e9, c\u2019est celui que le Seigneur recommande.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10","name":"2 Corinthiens 10","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.11.1","name":"2 Corinthiens 11:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.11.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Cor.10.17","name":"2 Corinthiens 10:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Cor.10.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbb308a32.71318147');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbb308a32.71318147\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbb308a32.71318147","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbb308a32.71318147'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbb308a32.71318147\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0